<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="{{ page_description | default: shop.description }}">
  <title>{{ page_title | default: shop.name }}</title>

  <link rel="icon" href="{{ 'favicon.ico' | asset_url }}" sizes="any">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Red+Hat+Display:wght@700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  {%- comment -%}
    CRITICAL: content_for_header injects Shopify's native tracking:
    - Meta CAPI (server-side)
    - Google Ads Enhanced Conversions
    - Shopify Analytics
    - Checkout tracking
    - Customer event pixels
    This is THE reason you moved to Shopify. Do NOT remove this.
  {%- endcomment -%}
  {{ content_for_header }}
</head>
<body>
  {{ content_for_layout }}
</body>
</html>
